2011-09-09T07:59:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-09/harmony-electron-august-sales-fall-18-30-table-8182-tt.html
HARMONY ELECTRON said unconsolidated sales
in August fell 18.30% to NT$389,035,000 from NT$476,168,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  8/2011           8/2010
Sales            389,035          476,168    
YOY%             -18.30%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           3,692,254        3,382,723   
YOY%              9.15%  
=================================================================
 